page.title: 13FREE TIME ON ST.MARY'S
page.content: MORE LIFESTYLE. OUR FREE TIME,HOUSES AND SHOPPING Later we asked some more people how many times a week they went shopping, the most day was Thursday the least day was Sunday. Presently we asked people what house they live in.The top answer people gave us was a ordinary house,the least number of people said guest houses,cottage,chalet and hotel. We asked people about there pets,the most popular pet was a doggie the least was a bird.Next we moved on to spare time the most people did was boating the least was watching T.V.,drinking,drama,al sorts,relaxing, photography and spending money.
